</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c462c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/b/15"><num value="15">(15)</num><content> In the case of large chickpeas, $14.00 per hundredweight.</content>
