</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4630-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/b/19"><num value="19">(19)</num><content> In the case of honey, $0.69 per pound.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4631-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/b/20"><num value="20">(20)</num><content> In the case of peanuts, $355 per ton.</content>
</paragraph>
