<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idf04c4632-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> 2026 through 2031 crop years</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of each of the 2026 through 2031 crop years, the loan rate for a marketing assistance loan under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s9031">section 9031 of this title</ref> for a loan commodity shall be equal to the following:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4633-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/c/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> In the case of wheat, $3.72 per bushel.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4634-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/c/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> In the case of corn, $2.42 per bushel.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4635-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/c/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> In the case of grain sorghum, $2.42 per bushel.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf04c4636-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9032/c/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> In the case of barley, $2.75 per bushel.</content>
